OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778193331
OL,3,CTechnical issue causes major delays
OL,4,Cand cancellations on railways
OL,6,FTrain services across southern England
OL,7,Fare severely delayed or cancelled, due
OL,8,Fto a fault with a radio system.
OL,10,FSouth Western Railway and GTR have
OL,11,Fsaid the issue relates to how train
OL,12,Fdrivers and signallers communicate.
OL,13,FThey are warning passengers that
OL,14,Fservices may be delayed by up to 90
OL,15,Fminutes, or not run at all.
OL,17,FThe affected operators also include
OL,18,FCrossCountry, Gatwick Express, Great
OL,19,FWestern Railway, London Overground and
OL,20,FThameslink.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
