CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778193331
OL,3,CTechnical issue causes major delays
OL,4,Cand cancellations on railways
OL,6,FDisruption began shortly before 9am on
OL,7,FThursday. But shortly before 11am,
OL,8,FNetwork Rail told ITV Meridian the
OL,9,Ffault was now fixed and services
OL,10,Fshould return to normal.
OL,12,FHowever, rail operators are warning
OL,13,Fthat disruption will continue for the
OL,14,Frest of Thursday. Disruption, as of
OL,15,F11am on Thursday, is particularly
OL,16,Fintense in the Portsmouth and
OL,17,FChichester areas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
