PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778193331
OL,3,CTechnical issue causes major delays
OL,4,Cand cancellations on railways
OL,6,FGovia Thameslink Railway, which runs
OL,7,Fservices under the Southern,
OL,8,FThameslink and Great Nothern brands,
OL,9,Fwarned it was curtailing routes due to
OL,10,Fthe disruption.
OL,12,FThe operator says Southern Services
OL,13,Fwill not run between some stations,
OL,14,Fwhich particular disruption between
OL,15,FChichester and Havant.
OL,17,FThe operator warned the following
OL,18,Froutes are particularly affected:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
