PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778193331
OL,3,CTechnical issue causes major delays
OL,4,Cand cancellations on railways
OL,6,FA GTR spokesperson said: "Due to a
OL,7,Ffault with the radio communication
OL,8,Fsystem between trains and signallers,
OL,9,Four services aren't running west of
OL,10,FChichester, at the moment.
OL,12,F"There's ticket acceptance on local
OL,13,Fbuses and we're advising passengers to
OL,14,Fcheck online before they travel for
OL,15,Fthe latest information. We're sorry
OL,16,Ffor the disruption this will cause to
OL,17,Fpeople's journeys this morning."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
