PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778193331
OL,3,CTechnical issue causes major delays
OL,4,Cand cancellations on railways
OL,6,FA Network Rail spokesperson said: "Due
OL,7,Fto issues with radio communications,
OL,8,Ftrain services in the South West and
OL,9,FSouth have been subject to some delays
OL,10,Fthis morning.
OL,12,F"Staff have worked to resolve the
OL,13,Ffault, and train services are now
OL,14,Freturning to normal. We apologise to
OL,15,Fpassengers for the disruption caused
OL,16,Fto their journeys this morning."
