PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778193331
OL,3,CTechnical issue causes major delays
OL,4,Cand cancellations on railways
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Great Western Railway,
OL,7,Fwhich runs services between Paddington
OL,8,Fand the South West and Wales, warned
OL,9,Fits passengers its trains were running
OL,10,Fat reduced speeds on some lines.
OL,12,FOn its website, the operator said:
OL,13,F"Network Rail technicians are working
OL,14,Fto resolve the fault. We are able to
OL,15,Frun trains but have to do so at a
OL,16,Freduced speed on some lines, so there
OL,17,Fwill be some delays."
OL,19,FThis is a developing story, more to
OL,20,Ffollow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
